        <title type="html"><![CDATA[CF476A Dreamoon and Stairs]]></title>
        <id>https://https://blackwhite0601.github.io/post/cf476a-dreamoon-and-stairs/</id>
        <link href="https://https://blackwhite0601.github.io/post/cf476a-dreamoon-and-stairs/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-10-02T02:24:17.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>通过题意可以发现，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span></span></span></span> 最大为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span></span></span></span> （一步一步跳），最小为 $n / 2 + n % 2 $ （两步两步跳），可以直接枚举在这个范围内的 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span></span></span></span> ，找出 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">m</span></span></span></span> 的倍数输出，代码如下：</p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
using namespace std;
int n,m;
int main(){
	scanf(&quot;%d%d&quot;,&amp;n,&amp;m);
	for(int i=(n/2)+(n%2);i&lt;=n;i++)
		if(i%m==0){
			printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;,i);
			return 0;
		}
	puts(&quot;-1&quot;);
	return 0;
}
</code></pre>
]]></content>
